{"tid":2501145,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台：美國國務院對蔡玉玲判刑感失望　聲稱蔡玉玲只是做好工作","createTime":"2021-04-23T07:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T07:19:15.000Z","uid":290404,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"87f34a1866d6c446cbe34fe2a2000e85ff2b8978","tid":2501145,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:18:34.000Z","msg":"美國國務院發言人普賴斯對涉嫌作出虛假陳述的香港電台節目《鏗鏘集－7.21誰主真相》編導蔡玉玲的判刑表示極度失望，聲稱蔡玉玲只是「做好自己的工作」，她最近奪得「金堯如新聞自由獎」，獎項肯定她對新聞自由的「重要貢獻」，而新聞自由是受《中英聯合聲明》保障。<br />\n<br />\n蔡玉玲因跟進採訪元朗7.21事件，就車牌資料查冊，其後被警方拘捕，西九龍裁判法院昨日裁定她兩項作出虛假陳述罪成，共罰款6000元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1587350-20210423.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1587350-20210423.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzlmNgp3wQ%2BT5fJEe%2BG4C8OY%3D&h=a7e86707\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1587350-20210423.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d455d771\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1587350-20210423.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"0f368172cac9e23f0f56b6c5e5dcee2cf570ede0","tid":2501145,"uid":293307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:19:15.000Z","msg":"你個名"}]}